{"tid":134744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【夢熊出冊】一出嚟爆大鑊？ 即晚上《光明頂》做嘉賓","createTime":"2017-02-25T17:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T09:17:03.000Z","uid":35790,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd57a0df59ab972a97facfdc3d7a1c1ad5ef93c","tid":134744,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:02:10.000Z","msg":"【夢熊出冊】一出嚟爆大鑊？ 即晚上《光明頂》做嘉賓<br />\n<br />\n2017-02-26 00:02:45 HKT&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n劉夢熊明天出獄，重獲自由。據了解，明早將有親人及保釣人士到場迎接劉出獄，先返回寓所稍事休息，晚上會出席電台節目《光明頂》任嘉賓；翌日晚上已相約民主黨劉慧卿、單仲楷等各界友好，在尖沙咀晚飯「洗塵」。<br />\n<br />\n一般情況下，在囚人士出獄前一晚會被通知執拾好個人物品，出獄當天早上起床梳洗、吃早餐，隨後會見監獄監督，由監督告知可以離開，之後將在懲教員陪伴下前往更衣，並領回入獄時交出的隨身私人物品，俗稱「包頭」。在點算、收取在囚期間工作糧金後，再經保安職員搜身，便可由職員帶到大閘離開，重獲自由。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"a1f268a3815f6cf7a8e5f461ff36430ee137e3ff","tid":134744,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439334117d988dd154204e9fd76118aa93225b2d","tid":134744,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a17920946608ad7318bb55a197f4277df7af52d","tid":134744,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3f58fbff1a0e9a8362026268fffa88fe067ac9","tid":134744,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T20:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0a561a0a23581a505a8485f89e6e9aae4f7043","tid":134744,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T20:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkg